title: Essential Chicago Blues(1997)[.MP3@320kbs]
description:
House of Blues ~ Essential Chicago Blues (Vol. 1)

Artist: Various Artists 
Format: (.mp3)/EAC @ 320kbs 
Release Year: 1997 
Record Label: House Of Blues 

This two disc set contains cuts by Bo Diddley, Otis Rush, Little Walter, Hound Dog Taylor, 
Muddy Waters (alternate take of "Hoochie Coochie Man"), J.B. Lenoir, Buddy Guy, 
Willie Mabon, Sonny Boy Williamson, Junior Wells, Howlin' Wolf, Jimmy Reed, J.B. Hutto, 
Eddie Taylor, Earl Hooker, and Big John Wrencher. There are also re-cuts by Otis Spann, 
Willie Dixon, Billy Boy Arnold, Hubert Sumlin,Son Seals, Carey Bell, Pinetop Perkins, 
Eddy Clearwater, Eddie C. Campbell, Jimmy Dawkins, John Primer, James Cotton, and Koko Taylor.
